            <head>"AN EARTH SONG"</head>

            <lg>
               <l enjamb="no">It’s an earth song,</l>
               <l enjamb="no">And I’ve been waiting long for an earth song.</l>
               <l enjamb="no">It’s a spring song,—</l>
               <l enjamb="no">And I’ve been waiting long for a spring song.</l>
            </lg>
            <lg>
               <l enjamb="yes">Strong as the shoots of a new plant</l>
               <l enjamb="yes">Strong as the bursting of new buds</l>
               <l enjamb="yes">Strong as the coming of the first child from its mother’s</l>
               <l enjamb="no">womb.</l>
            </lg>
            <lg>
               <l enjamb="no">It’s an earth song,</l>
               <l enjamb="no">A body-song,</l>
               <l enjamb="no">A spring song,—</l>
               <l enjamb="no">I have been waiting long for this spring song.</l>
            </lg>
            <byline>-Langston Hughes</byline>

         </div>
